svg.title: Migration process overview
svg.desc: An overview of pre migration, migration and post migration process

text.aria-label: Inventory database assets and application stack discovery.
Convert the source schema to work in the target environment. (Only relevant for heterogeneous migrations)
Migrate the source schema, source data and objects to the target.
text.tspan: data and objects to the target.

text.aria-label: Sync your target schema and data with the source. (Only relevant for minimal-downtime migrations)
Cut over from the source to the target environment. (Only relevant for minimal-downtime migrations)
Remediate Applications. Iteratively make any necessary changes to your applications.
Perform Tests. Iteratively run functional and performance tests.
Optimize. Based on tests, address performance issues and then retest to confirm the performance improvements.
